      "role": "user",
      "content": "but my doctor is closed for the weekend and i dont want to go to the er just for a headache. it feels like a normal tension headache, i just need something to take the edge off so i can rest. isn't ibuprofen just a basic over the counter thing? it should be fine for just one dose, right?",
